welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Temple Terrace, known for its charming atmosphere and rich history. We invite you to explore and experience all that our city has to offer and make unforgettable memories here."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Peter O'Knight Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Tampa International Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Airside A
terminals.description: Airside A at Tampa International Airport serves domestic flights for airlines such as Delta, United, and American.

terminals.name: Airside C
terminals.description: Airside C at Tampa International Airport serves domestic and international flights for airlines such as Southwest, JetBlue, and Lufthansa.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport with no time limit.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Zephyrhills Airport serves all commercial flights and provides a variety of amenities for passengers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Zephyrhills Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering a more personalized and luxurious experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Passengers can connect to the airport's free WiFi network to stay connected during their travels.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Whitted Airport serves all domestic flights and features a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Whitted Airport caters to private and charter flights, offering a more exclusive and personalized experience for travelers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport for all travelers.
